<p>The <code>bold</code> function wraps the value in <code>&lt;b&gt;</code> tags.</p>

<h2>Basic Usage</h2>
<pre>{open}'important' | bold{close}</pre>
<p>Result: {'important' | bold}</p>

<h2>Chained Examples</h2>
<pre>{open}'hello world' | upper | bold{close}</pre>
<p>Result: {'hello world' | upper | bold}</p>

<pre>{open}'  warning  ' | trim | bold{close}</pre>
<p>Result: {'  warning  ' | trim | bold}</p>

<h2>With Users</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  {open}$name | bold{close}: {open}$email{close}
{open}/users{close}</pre>
<p>Bold names:</p>
{users}
  {$name | bold}: {$email}<br>
{/users}

<h2>Complex Chain</h2>
<pre>{open}'john.doe' | replace('.', ' ') | capitalize | bold{close}</pre>
<p>Result: {'john.doe' | replace('.', ' ') | capitalize | bold}</p>
